Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.45,0:00:04.74,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Infatuation isn't something \Nyou confirm in a moment.} Není to něco, co by sis mohla potvrdit během chvíle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.70,0:00:09.44,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Feelings like those\Nhit you naturally over time.} Takovéhle pocity přicházejí postupně.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:12.69,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{So don't rush it, okay?} Tak na to netlač, dobře?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.47,0:02:03.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Even if I get through these finals,}I když se dostanu přes tyhle zkoušky,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.43,0:02:06.31,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{there's the internal advancement exam \Nright after winter break.} tak hned po zimních prázdninách jsou další.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.92,0:02:09.18,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Why does everyone else \Nseem so relaxed about it?} Tak proč všichni vypadají tak bezstarostně?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.02,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{Compared to external college exams,} V porovnání s univerzitními zkouškami,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.02,0:02:14.53,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{the internal one is easy and basically a formality of sorts.} jsou tyhle školní snadné, a jsou vlastně jen formalitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.77,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{No one here is gonna sweat it at this point.} Nikdo se tady z toho nebude stresovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.57,0:02:19.99,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{It might be easy for you guys,} Pro vás to může být snadné,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:23.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{but I'm not going to have a moment to relax over New Year's.} ale já nebudu mít v průběhu nového roku ani chvíli na odpočinek.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.55,0:02:27.33,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{Then do what you can to get better.} No, tak to se musíš zlepšit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:30.51,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{You want to take it easy on Christmas \Nand New Year's at least, right?} Chceš toho mít na Vánoce\N a na Nový rok co nejméně, ne? { Tady si nejsem jistej :C }
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.51,0:02:32.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Eh, Vánoce...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:35.66,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Nemáš žádné plány?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.66,0:02:37.96,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Samozřejmě že ne.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.27,0:02:41.26,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Ty? Půjdeš na radne s Kariu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.32,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Jo, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.54,0:02:47.81,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{Where do you even go for Christmas?} Kam se na Vánoce chodí?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:49.44,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.44,0:02:52.52,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{I said I'd take her somewhere, \Nbut I can't think of anything!} Řekl jsem, že ji někam vezmu, ale vůbec nevím kam!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:55.44,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{I want to do something she'll love,} Chci dělat něco, co se jí bude líbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.44,0:02:59.65,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{but I'm racking my brains and not getting anywhere.} ale prostě nedokážu nic pořádného vymyslet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.31,0:03:02.74,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{I need your grown-up advice!}Potřebuji tvoji dospěláckou radu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.74,0:03:04.08,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Grown-up?}Dospěláckou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.08,0:03:08.47,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{You seem to really understand\Nhow girls think.} Zdá se, že víš jak holky přemýšlejí.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.47,0:03:10.45,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I really don't.} To opravdu nevím.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:16.10,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{But if you want "grown-up," does that mean you're ready?} Ale jestli fakt chceš "dospěláckou" radu, znamená to snad, že jsi připraven?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:16.83,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.80,0:03:21.84,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{To climb the stairs to adulthood, I mean.} Abys zdolal schody k dospělosti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:33.27,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Just do what you always do,\N and go where you like.} Prostě udělej co vždycky \Na jděte někam, kde to máte rádi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.10,0:03:35.98,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{You were made for each other.} Jste pro sebe stvoření.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.98,0:03:37.78,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{No need to stress about it now.} Nemusíš se nad tím stresovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.77,0:03:40.48,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{You can have fun wherever, right?} Můžete se bavit kdekoliv, ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:41.78,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,No, to jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:44.32,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Můžeme, ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:47.61,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{Made for each other?}Stvořeni pro sebe?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:49.53,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{You're too pure!} Jsi moc nevinný! {Nemyslím si že by znělo dobře "jsi moc čistý" :D }
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.28,0:03:54.36,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,No a co ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.75,0:03:55.47,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:59.78,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{Aren't you gonna ask Hishiro-san\N anywhere for Christmas?} Ty nikam Hishiro na Vánoce nepozveš?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:00.58,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.14,0:04:03.88,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{I mean, you both love each other, right?} Máte se přece rádi, nebo ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:05.92,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Don't go jumping to conclusions!} Nedělej ukvapené závěry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.01,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{Kariu seemed pretty sure.}Kariu si tím byla dost jistá.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:12.10,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{Tamarai-san said she saw you two getting close at the cultural festival, too.} Tamarai zase řekla, že vás na festivalu viděla spolu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:22.59,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{You two should just start going out, too.} Taky byste si spolu měli někam zajít.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:24.20,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{That's not for you to decide.} O tom nerozhoduj.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.31,0:04:29.38,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{It's not as easy for me as it was for you.} Pro mě to není tak snadné jako pro vás dva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:45.31,Flashback Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{I mean, you both love each other, right?} Máte se přece rádi, nebo ne?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:49.97,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Me? Sure.} Já? Určitě.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:53.56,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I wasn't expecting anyone to think Hishiro-san felt the same way, though.}Nečekal jsem, že by si někdo mohl myslet, že to Hishiro taky tak cítí.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:57.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Dobré ráno, Hishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.49,0:05:13.45,Italics Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Co...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:16.24,Italics Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Co...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.91,0:05:18.28,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Co to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.00,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hishi—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:25.94,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Co se to děje?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:31.27,Main Dialogue,Kariu,0,0,0,,{So, what's gotten into you today, Hishiro?} Co to do tebe dneska vjelo, Hishiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.36,0:05:35.54,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{You mean about Kaizaki-san?} Myslíš to s Kaizakim?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:38.73,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,{You're awfully perceptive today.} Dneska jsi nějak vnímavá.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:41.38,Main Dialogue,Kariu,0,0,0,,Takže? Co se děje?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:50.03,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{It seems my stupidity with regards to emotions has grown worse lately.}Vypadá to, že se moje nechápavost emocí ještě zhoršila.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.23,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,Nechápavost?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:53.62,Main Dialogue,Kariu,0,0,0,,{That's just a Hishiroism.} To je jen Hishiroismus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.75,Main Dialogue,Kariu,0,0,0,,{She's saying she doesn't understand \Nher own feelings anymore.}Říká, že vůbec nerozumí svým vlastním pocitům.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.61,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,Páni, Reno.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.94,0:06:03.08,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{So I tried linking arms, and a few other things.}Tak jsem se snažila spojit ruce a další věci. {Mluví o tom jak ho chytila za ruku? }
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.59,0:06:06.62,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{But I stayed stupid\N and couldn't figure it out.} Ale furt jsem blbá a nemůžu to pochopit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.19,0:06:12.80,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{This morning, I impulsively thought to put some distance between us.}Dneska ráno jsem mezi námi impulzivně vytvořila mezeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.36,0:06:18.30,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{I thought that might help me gain a different perspective.} Myslela jsem, že mi to pomůže získat novou perspektivu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:26.06,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{But maybe some other emotion\N is spurring me on.} ale nejspíš mě to svádí k jiným emocím.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:28.32,Main Dialogue,Kariu,0,0,0,,Jiným emocím?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.32,Main Dialogue,Kariu,0,0,0,,{What do you think that is?}K jakým myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:39.45,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Nevím.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:42.25,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,{So close! So close, Hishiron!}Tak blízko! Byla jsi tak blízko, Hishiron!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:44.59,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,{If you've gotten that far,\Nyou already know—} Když už jsi zašla tak daleko, tak už to musíš vědět-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.86,0:06:46.96,Main Dialogue,Kariu,0,0,0,,Hishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:50.21,Main Dialogue,Kariu,0,0,0,,{You can't just wriggle out of this with an "I don't know."} Nemůžeš se z toho vykroutit prostým "Já nevím."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:53.22,Main Dialogue,Kariu,0,0,0,,{You're only one step away!} Jsi už jen krůček od toho!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:55.72,Main Dialogue,Kariu,0,0,0,,Tak se snaž.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.31,0:07:03.56,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{Hang in there... Arata...} Vydrž to... Arato...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:07.36,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Right back... at you...}Koukni se... na sebe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:09.15,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{Hang in there... me...}Snaž se... Já...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.67,0:07:11.72,Main Dialogue,Both,0,0,0,,Brr!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.72,0:07:14.82,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{The girls... get basketball... in the gym?}Holky... mají basket... v tělocvičně?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:16.16,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{Lucky them!} Šťastlivci.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:18.70,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,Taková zima.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:24.04,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,{Pass! Over here} Přihraj! Tady!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.57,0:07:30.10,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,{Suddenly, Rena's the voice of authority, huh?}Najednou má Rena hlas autority, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.10,0:07:31.33,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{That's nothing new.}To není žádná novinka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.33,0:07:32.56,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,Pravda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.56,0:07:36.09,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,{But ever since she started dating Oga-kun, it's like she's gotten all mature.} Ale od doby, co začala chodit s Ogou, jako by dospěla.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.31,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,{She got asked out on a Christmas date, too.}Dokonce ji i pozval na Vánoce ven.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:42.90,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,{But just to, like, where they always go.} Ale nakonec půjdou tam, kam chodí vždycky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:44.69,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,Nadávala na něj s úsměvem na rtech.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:46.89,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Rande?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.31,0:07:49.72,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,{Yeah! I mean, it is Christmas.} Jo! Přeci jen to jsou Vánoce.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.27,0:07:51.20,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Pěkná střela.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.28,0:07:54.31,Main Dialogue,Girl,0,0,0,,Tady.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.32,0:07:55.66,Main Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,{Get back on defense!}Zpátky do obrany.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.66,0:07:58.51,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,{Why don't you try \Nasking Kaizaki-kun out, too?} Proč taky Kaizakiho někam nepozveš?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:00.39,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,Na rande?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:02.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Rande?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.86,0:08:06.04,Main Dialogue,Tamarai,0,0,0,,Rande.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.08,Main Dialogue,Oga,0,0,0,,{I'll nab us some seats.}Zaberu nám nějaká místa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:18.93,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Jasně.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:25.59,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I'm sure she's just overthinking things again.}Určitě o tom zase příliš přemýšlela.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.19,0:08:30.40,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{But we won't get anywhere close to going out as things stand.}Ale takhle, jak se věci mají, se nijak nesblížíme.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:33.47,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Wait, why would we go out?} Počkat, proč bychom vlastně měli?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:35.86,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Why am I letting Oga get to me?}Proč jsem Ogovi dovolill mi tu myšlenku nasadit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:43.13,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Hishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.06,0:08:46.48,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Co? Tentokrát neutekla?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:50.71,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kaizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:54.25,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{Do you have plans for the 25th?} Máš nějaké plány na 25.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.88,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,25.?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:59.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{You mean... of this month?}Myslíš... tenhle měsíc?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:00.76,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Nemám.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.17,0:09:04.26,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{Then go out with me that day.}Tak pojď se mnou ven.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.53,0:09:05.51,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Co?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.10,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Na Ra...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.42,0:09:09.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,"Ra"?
