Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.81,0:11:02.47,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Vánoce, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:07.38,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Rande?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.94,0:11:09.44,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,To je super.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:11.69,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{It's not like I asked her.} Já jí nepozval.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:13.77,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{And turning her down seems rude.}A odmítnout ji mi přišlo hrubé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.77,0:11:16.25,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{It is Hishiro-san asking, after all.} Takže se zeptala Hishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:18.51,Flashback Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{So I can go?}Takže můžu jít?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.51,0:11:22.65,Flashback Italics Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Of course. From a ReLIFE perspective, \Nit'll be a valuable experience.} Samozřejmě. Z hlediska ReLIFE to bude neocenitelná zkušenost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.78,0:11:26.13,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{From a ReLIFE perspective...}Z hlediska ReLIFE...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.53,0:11:31.04,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{This high school version of you \Nis just an illusion.}Tahle tvá středoškolská podoba je jen iluze.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:36.19,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{So this Christmas will become an illusion for Hishiro-san?}Takže se tyhle Vánoce pro Hishiro stanou iluzí?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:38.30,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Je to v pořádku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:44.29,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Even if those memories vanish, \Nother things will remain.} I když vzpomínky na tebe zmizí, ostatní zůstane.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.17,0:11:48.14,Flashback Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{I guess you could call it\Nthe mark that you left on them.} Dalo by se pak říct, že jsi v nich zanechal stopu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.27,0:11:51.35,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Omlouvám se, Hishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.81,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Your Christmas'll be ruined forever.} Tvoje Vánoce budou navždy zničené.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.24,0:11:56.59,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Ale já...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:06.28,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{...was happy you invited me.} ...byl moc šťastný, že jsi mě pozvala.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.28,0:12:17.29,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Hishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.85,0:12:21.42,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{It's still 30 minutes early.} Jsi tu o půl hodiny dřív.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:25.67,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{I'm the one who invited you,\Nso I can hardly be late.}To já tě pozvala, tak bych těžko mohla přijít pozdě.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:28.85,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{You're quite early yourself.} Ty tu jsi taky brzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:30.85,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Velmi profesionální.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:33.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{W-Well, you said it was a date, and uh...} N-no, řekla jsi, že je to rande, takže...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:36.15,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{That's a cute outfit!} Ten outfit ti sluší!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.32,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{Kariu-san and Tamarai-san\N picked it out for me.}Kariu a Tamarai mi to pomohly vybrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:44.33,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah? Well, it looks good.} Jo? Sluší ti to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.98,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Děkuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:49.55,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{So, uh, what's the plan?} Takže, co je v plánu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:55.06,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{I researched standard date routes} Udělala jsem si výzkum o rande
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.06,0:12:58.25,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{and prepared a number of suitable candidates.} a připravila několik vhodných variant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:01.34,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{And printed them out!} A vytiskla si je!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.64,0:13:05.36,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{But in the end, I didn't know what was best.}Ale nakonec nevím, co bude nejlepší.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.80,0:13:12.35,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Thanks. You put a lot of thought into this, huh?} Díky. Hodně jsi o tom přemýšlela, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:13.92,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Koukněme...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.92,0:13:18.43,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Oh, hey, there's an event going on. Should we start with that?}Oh, tady je nějaká akce. Chceš začít s tím?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.42,0:13:21.35,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:29.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Mimochodem, proč zrovna 25.?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.60,0:13:35.49,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I mean, the classic date night \Nis the 24th, Christmas Eve.} Chci říct, že běžně se na rande chodí na Štědrý večer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.55,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Vážně?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:42.68,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{Everyone says "Christmas date," so I never considered it could be any other day.}Všichni říkají "Vánoční rande," tak mě nikdy nenapadlo, že to můžou být i ostatní dny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.68,0:13:43.87,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Omlouvám se.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.87,0:13:46.19,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{No, if you're fine with it, I am.} Ne, to je v pohodě, nevadí mi to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.55,0:13:49.63,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Yesterday might have been way too crowded.} A včera to tu nejspíš bylo přeplněné.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.73,0:13:57.61,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Je ti zima?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:14:03.36,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{No. Kariu-san and Tamarai-san also\N taught me how to fight the cold.}Ne. Kariu a Tamarai mě naučily, jak bojovat se zimou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.62,0:14:08.37,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I guess you girls can really look out for each other.} Hádám, že vy holky se toho od sebe můžete hodně naučit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:09.76,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Jo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:12.96,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{They're friends who can be relied upon.} Jsou to přátelé na které se dá spolehnout.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:31.26,Main Dialogue,Onoya,0,0,0,,{Should we really be chilling here like this?}Vážně bychom tu takhle měli odpočívat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.32,0:14:37.34,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{They'll be walking around the mall for\N a while. Shouldn't be a problem.} Nějakou chvíli se budou procházet po obchoďáku. Nemělo by to vadit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:38.80,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Mimochodem...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.84,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{And that's when Oga went full...}A pak, když se Oga najedl....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:45.61,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Jsou Vánoce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:53.85,Main Dialogue,Onoya,0,0,0,,{You say that, but you actually just\Nwanna be on a date with me, right?}Sice říkáš tohle, ale ve skutečnosti jsi se mnou chtěl jít na rande, že?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.85,0:14:55.40,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Please, listen to yourself.} Poslouchej se někdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:04.36,Main Dialogue,Onoya,0,0,0,,{They'll both forget this date, too, right?} Oba na tohle rande zapomenou, co?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.58,0:15:17.49,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{They will, but that won't mean \Nit never happened.} Ano, ale to neznamená, že k němu nedošlo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.06,0:15:21.44,Main Dialogue,Onoya,0,0,0,,Co děláš?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.15,sign_22093_215_Arata_Kaizaki,Top,0,0,0,,Kaizaki Arata
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.15,sign_22093_216_Good_time__to_ca,Blue,0,0,0,,Můžu zavolat?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.44,0:15:22.15,sign_22093_217_Go_ahead_,Green,0,0,0,,Do toho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:25.66,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{Oh, just being a busybody.} Jsem jen všetečnej. {dá se to tak? }
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:32.84,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Yoake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.02,0:15:36.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Co myslíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.84,0:15:40.23,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Looks like that sorry cat sticker.}Vypadá to jako kočičí přívěšek.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.23,0:15:44.70,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{Would you prefer a more subdued design?}Upřednostňoval bys méně nápadný design?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:49.70,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{As a present. It is Christmas.}Je to dárek. Jsou přece Vánoce.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.56,0:16:00.45,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{If that's what you picked out for me, then that's what I want.} Jestli jsi to vybrala pro mě,\N tak je to to, co chci.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:12.79,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Um, promiňte.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:14.94,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Vezmu si tohle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.65,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,A já si vezmu tohle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.85,0:16:21.62,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{A Christmas gift from me, too.} Vánoční dárek ode mě.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:24.14,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{And a birthday present.}A narozeninový dárek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:27.74,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Happy birthday, Hishiro-san.} Všechno nejlepší, Hishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.14,0:16:32.63,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Děkuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.22,sign_23814_234_Today_is__Hishir,New Text,0,0,0,,{Today is\N Hishiro-san's birthday.} Dnes má Hishiro narozeniny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:51.61,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{When is your birthday?} Kdy máš narozeniny ty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.98,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Taky ti něco dám.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.98,0:16:57.54,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about it. It's in August.}S tím si nedělej starosti. Je to v srpnu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.54,0:17:00.11,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{Oh, I totally missed it, then.} Oh, to jsem prošvihla.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:02.33,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{Then we'll have to...} Tak to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:07.09,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{...celebrate next year.}...oslavíme příští rok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.77,0:17:23.90,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Příští rok...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:26.73,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, Promiň.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:28.33,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,To nic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:32.83,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I mean, this year's almost over.} Tenhle rok je skoro u konce.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.83,0:17:35.60,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{And I was thinking how next year\Nwould probably fly by, too.} A přemýšlel jsem, jak uběhne příští rok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:39.57,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Just as this year did for me.}Tak jako pro mě uběhl tento rok.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.41,0:17:42.90,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Tento... rok?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.74,0:17:48.05,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I transferred in, met you,} Přestoupil jsem, potkal tě
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:51.05,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{and went through so much with Oga and the others, too.}a s Ogou a s ostatními jsem toho taky tolik prožil.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:55.04,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,A akce byly super brutální.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:18:01.05,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{There have been lots of things to think about, worry over, hesitate...} Byla tu spousta věcí nad kterými přemýšlet, trápit se jimi, váhat...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.89,0:18:03.82,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{...but every day was a blast.} ...ale každý den byl zábavný.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:07.03,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{When I grow up,} Myslím, že až budu dospělý,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:12.45,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I think I'll look back at this year \Nas a really special one.} zhodnotím tento rok jako velice speciální. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.94,0:18:23.33,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Is something wrong?} Děje se něco?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.52,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,N-Ne...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.14,0:18:31.38,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Cítím to stejně.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:38.17,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{I won't ever forget today, either.}Nechci na dnešek zapomenout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:18:57.46,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Hishiro-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.46,0:18:58.33,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Jo?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.01,0:19:01.44,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Můžeme se projít ještě kousek?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:16.09,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I'm in love with Hishiro-san.} Zamiloval jsem se do Hishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.40,0:19:22.32,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Ale...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.74,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I can't force that on her any more.} Nemůžu jí to vnucovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.87,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{I'll vanish eventually.\N My feelings don't matter.}Nakonec zmizím. Na mých pocitech nezáleží.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.89,0:19:32.89,Flashback Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{I won't ever forget today, either.} Nechci na dnešek zapomenout.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:37.02,Italics Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Ale já...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.02,0:19:38.94,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Hishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.23,0:19:52.43,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Promiň.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:54.56,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Nemáš se za co omlouvat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.05,0:19:59.20,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{But I was the one who grabbed your arm and asked you to hug me...} Ale já byla ta, která tě chytla \Nza ruku a chtěla po tobě objetí...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.20,0:20:02.50,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{I have no right to do this\Nafter asking so much of you.} Na tohle nemám právo, \Nkdyž jsem po tobě chtěla tak moc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.35,0:20:05.40,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Já... prostě...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:10.26,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Vážně nerozumím sama sobě.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:16.28,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{The more you're on my mind, the less I understand what to do.} Čím víc o tobě přemýšlím, tím méně rozumím tomu, co mám dělat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.32,0:20:19.72,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Přemýšlíš?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:26.92,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Does that mean you have feelings \Nthat are different from before?} Myslíš tím, že tvé pocity jsou jiné než předtím?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:36.18,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{Sorry. I'm really not sure.} Promiň. Já fakt nevím.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.18,0:20:38.03,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Moje mysl je zamotaná.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:42.10,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{It'll take time to work it out.} Potřebuju nějaký čas to zpracovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:43.71,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{Pay it no attention.} Nevšímej si toho.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:50.05,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Jsem natom stejně.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.26,0:20:55.94,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{You're on my mind, too.}Taky o tobě furt přemýšlím.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:20:59.94,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Maybe not in the same way, though.}I když možná ne tak jako ty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.15,0:21:07.28,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Miluji tě, Hishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.52,0:21:12.43,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.97,0:21:14.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Omlouvám se, já...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.52,0:21:15.46,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Já...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.46,0:21:19.52,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,{Yeah, I know, \Nthat came outta nowhere! Uh...}Ano, já vím, bylo to moc náhle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.52,0:21:20.56,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Kaizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.17,Main Dialogue,Kaizaki,0,0,0,,Ano?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:27.08,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,{I don't think my feelings are any different.} Nemyslím si, že se mé pocity v něčem liší.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.18,0:21:30.27,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Jsou stejné.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.74,0:21:33.47,Main Dialogue,Hishiro,0,0,0,,Cítím to stejně jako ty, Kaizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.17,0:23:40.18,Next Episode,Screen,0,0,0,,Další epizoda
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.92,0:23:28.55,Main Dialogue,Onoya,0,0,0,,{Just as every night is followed by dawn,} Stejně jako každou noc následuje svítání,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:31.75,Main Dialogue,Onoya,0,0,0,,{I want to believe that \Nevery rain eventually lets up.} chci věřit že každá přeháňka odezní.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.75,0:23:33.28,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,Co děláš?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:34.79,Main Dialogue,Onoya,0,0,0,,{A fair-weather charm.} Kouzlo počasí...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.14,0:23:36.70,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{I'll make one, too!}Taky jedno udělám!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.70,0:23:38.57,Main Dialogue,Ryo,0,0,0,,{It's our final act as their support.} Je to náš poslední čin jako jejich podpory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.57,0:23:39.38,Main Dialogue,Onoya,0,0,0,,Ano.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:41.38,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,
